          {
            "type": "TEXT",
            "data": "[]\n{\"com_grp_cd\":\"DR\",\"com_grp_cd_nm\":\"Dag Reprocess YN\",\"com_cd\":\"01\",\"com_cd_nm\":\"Y\",\"com_cd_desc\":\"Y면 Dag 재배치 활성화 , N이면 Dag 재배치 비활성화\",\"use_yn\":\"Y\",\"ver_no\":0}\njava.lang.ClassNotFoundException: org.mariadb.jdbc.Driver\n  at scala.reflect.internal.util.AbstractFileClassLoader.findClass(AbstractFileClassLoader.scala:72)\n  at java.base/java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:594)\n  at java.base/java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:527)\n  at java.base/java.lang.Class.forName0(Native Method)\n  at java.base/java.lang.Class.forName(Class.java:315)\n  ... 46 elided\n"
